    "title": "MSC India Advisory Limited is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Join the MSC India Advisory Limited family as a Warehouse Manager in Gurgaon. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout MSC India Advisory Limited:\nMSC India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MSC India Advisory Limited!",
